{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6d287895fa","title":"复饶激石电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d5259fcb5f","index":0,"year":1949,"month":9,"day":12,"articleId":"6d287895fa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"f21d474ac3","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指陈毅、刘晓、菜裕，当时分别任第三野战军兼华东军区司令员、中共中央上海局书记、第三野战军兼华东军区副司令员。"}],"contents":[{"id":"ac1e76e656","type":"title","text":"复饶激石电”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa"},{"id":"f21d474ac3","type":"paragraph","text":"饶淞石同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa"},{"id":"321487e0f9","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）完全同意你中佳电各项意见和办法。你们这样做，就有了全部的主动权。（二）我们所需要的正是这样的报告，此外不须做另外的综合报告。（三）关于华东局与上海市委分开及建立华东人民政府，待与陈、刘、菜商量后就可以做，你们可马上进行准备工作。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa"},{"id":"e67a04defe","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa"},{"id":"2c499e8e83","type":"paragraph","text":"申文","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa"},{"id":"9b4c5b6ffb","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]这是毛泽东对饶激石1949年9月9日关于上海与华东近况给毛泽东的报告的复电。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa"}],"page":{"id":"428367c282","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"6d287895fa","start":235,"end":235}}}},"__N_SSG":true}